					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Era of United States history in the 1780s</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Not to be confused with <a href="/wiki/Confederate_States_of_America" title="Confederate States of America">Confederate States of America</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox ib-country vcard"><tbody><tr><th colspan="2" class="infobox-above adr"><div class="fn org country-name">The United States of America</div></th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-subheader">1781–1789</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-image"><div class="noresize" style="display:table; width:100%;">
        <div style="display:table-cell; vertical-align:middle; padding-left:5px;">
            <div style="padding-bottom:3px;"><span class="mw-image-border" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_the_United_States_(1777%E2%80%931795).svg" class="mw-file-description" title="Flag of Confederation Period"><img alt="Thirteen star US flag" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/Flag_of_the_United_States_%281777%E2%80%931795%29.svg/125px-Flag_of_the_United_States_%281777%E2%80%931795%29.svg.png" decoding="async" width="125" height="66" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/Flag_of_the_United_States_%281777%E2%80%931795%29.svg/188px-Flag_of_the_United_States_%281777%E2%80%931795%29.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/19/Flag_of_the_United_States_%281777%E2%80%931795%29.svg/250px-Flag_of_the_United_States_%281777%E2%80%931795%29.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="1235" data-file-height="650" /></a></span></div>
            <div><a href="/wiki/Flag_of_the_United_States" title="Flag of the United States">Flag</a></div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:table-cell; vertical-align:middle; padding: 0px 5px;">
            <div style="padding-bottom:3px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Great_Seal_of_the_United_States_of_America_(1782).svg" class="mw-file-description" title="Seal of Confederation Period"><img alt="Seal of the United States" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e0/Great_Seal_of_the_United_States_of_America_%281782%29.svg/100px-Great_Seal_of_the_United_States_of_America_%281782%29.svg.png" decoding="async" width="100" height="100" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e0/Great_Seal_of_the_United_States_of_America_%281782%29.svg/150px-Great_Seal_of_the_United_States_of_America_%281782%29.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e0/Great_Seal_of_the_United_States_of_America_%281782%29.svg/200px-Great_Seal_of_the_United_States_of_America_%281782%29.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="512" data-file-height="512" /></a></span></div>
            <div><a href="/wiki/Great_Seal_of_the_United_States" title="Great Seal of the United States"> Seal</a></div>
        </div>
    </div></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data"><b>Motto:&#160;</b><i><a href="/wiki/E_pluribus_unum" title="E pluribus unum">E pluribus unum</a></i> (<a href="/wiki/Latin_language" class="mw-redirect" title="Latin language">Latin</a>)<br />"Out of many, one"</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data anthem"><b>Anthem:</b>&#160;None official</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data"><span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Frameless"><a href="/wiki/File:United_States_land_claims_and_cessions_1782-1802.png" class="mw-file-description" title="Map of the United States and territories after the Treaty of Paris (1783)"><img alt="Map of United States, changes in territory 1782=1802" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/34/United_States_land_claims_and_cessions_1782-1802.png/250px-United_States_land_claims_and_cessions_1782-1802.png" decoding="async" width="250" height="262" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/34/United_States_land_claims_and_cessions_1782-1802.png/375px-United_States_land_claims_and_cessions_1782-1802.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/34/United_States_land_claims_and_cessions_1782-1802.png/500px-United_States_land_claims_and_cessions_1782-1802.png 2x" data-file-width="747" data-file-height="782" /></a></span><div class="ib-country-map-caption">Map of the United States and territories after the Treaty of Paris (1783)</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Status</th><td class="infobox-data"><a href="/wiki/List_of_historical_unrecognized_states" class="mw-redirect" title="List of historical unrecognized states">Unrecognized state</a> (Until 1783)</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Capital</th><td class="infobox-data"><a href="/wiki/Philadelphia" title="Philadelphia">Philadelphia</a><br />(1781–1783)<br /><a href="/wiki/Princeton,_New_Jersey" title="Princeton, New Jersey">Princeton</a><br />(